  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC262">
          <l>maṟṟeṉ kiḷavi viṉaimāṟ ṟacainilai</l>
          <l>yappā liraṇṭeṉa moḻimaṉār pulavar.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/163/mode/1up">163</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ic cūttiram eṉṉutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, mēl tattaṅ kuṟippiṟ poruḷceykuvaṉa uṇarttiṉār; iṉi maṟṟu eṉpatōr iṭaiccol viṉaimāṟṟum acainilaiyumāy varum eṉpatu uṇarttukiṉṟār.
      </p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘iḵtu uṇ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟāṟku,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>‘maṟṟu uṇpal’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa viṉaimāṟṟu āyiṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
yāvarōṭāyiṉuñ collāṭāniṉṟu ‘maṟṟōmaṟṟu’ eṉṉum iṭaiyē; aḵtu acainilaik kaṭṭurai. (14)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n214/mode/1up">211</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i–ḷ. maṟṟeṉṉuñcol viṉaimāṟṟum acainilaiyumeṉa iraṇṭām. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u–m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘maṟṟaṟivā nalviṉai yāmiḷaiyam’<app><note>(nālaṭi. 9)</note></app></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻi aṟañceytal piṉṉaṟivāmeṉa akkālattu viṉaimāṟṟutalāṉ maṟṟeṉpatu viṉaimāṟṟiṉkaṇ vantatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Cena-cit2">
        <l>‘atumaṟṟavalaṅ koḷḷātu notumaṟkaluḻum’<app><note>(kuṟun. 12)</note></app></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉa acainilaiyāy vantatu. kaṭṭuraiyiṭaiyum maṟṟō eṉa acainilaiyāy varum.	(14)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/292/mode/1up">292</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/293/mode/1up">293</ref>.</p>
      <p>
itu, poruḷpaṭumāṟu macai nilaiyuṅ kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) maṟṟeṉ kiḷavi viṉaimāṟ ṟacainilai yappāliraṇṭeṉa moḻimaṉār pulavar – maṟṟeṉṉuñ col ‘muṉ colkiṉṟa toḻiya viṉi vēṟoṉṟeṉṉum poruṇmaiyum acainilaiyātalum eṉṉum akkūṟṟiraṇṭā meṉṟu kūṟuvar pulavareṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u–m) iṉi maṟṟoṉṟurai
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘<sic>maṟṟivām</sic> nalviṉai yāmiḷaiyam’</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘maṟṟuṅkūṭum maṉaimaṭi tuyilē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉat toḻiluṅ kālamu miṭamum paṟṟivarum.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Nacc-cit3">
         <l>‘atumaṟ ṟavalam koḷḷātu’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉpatu acai nilai
      </p>  
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Nacc-cit4">
        <l>‘uraiyāṭā niṉṟuḻip poruḷ kuṟiyātu</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
‘maṟṟō’ veṉavu macainilai varu,’ meṉpārumuḷar.
<term xml:lang="en">(14)</term>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n180/mode/1up">173</ref>.</p>
      <p>
oru poruḷaik kuṟitta iṭaiccol uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
i–ḷ: ― maṟṟu eṉṉumiṭaiccol oruviṉaiyai māṟṟutaṟ poruṭkaṇṇum, acainilaiyākiyum varum. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u-m: ―
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Tey-cit1">
        <l>maṟṟaṟivā nalviṉai yāmiḷaiyam<note place="foot">nālaṭi. 19</note></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻi maṟṟu eṉpatu piṉpu aṟivām eṉa akkālattuc ceykiṉṟa viṉaiyai māṟṟi niṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC262-Tey-cit2">
        <l>maṟṟaṭikaḷ kaṇṭaruḷic ceyka malaraṭikkīḻ<note place="foot">cīvaka 1873</note></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉṟavaḻi acainilai yāyiṟṟu.	[14]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
